595
00:40:55.954 --> 00:40:57.830
Whoa, hey. Uh, just a minute.

596
00:41:03.294 --> 00:41:04.754
I love it!

597
00:41:04.921 --> 00:41:06.923
Whee! It's easy!

598
00:41:07.006 --> 00:41:08.675
