605
00:41:23.773 --> 00:41:26.109
I... I did?

606
00:41:26.192 --> 00:41:29.195
Yeah. And so, I was like...

607
00:41:51.759 --> 00:41:55.013
Well, that's a lovely dream
you had there, Porsha.

608
00:41:55.138 --> 00:41:57.849
Um, okay, everybody, back
to first positions, please.

609
00:41:57.974 --> 00:41:58.975
Here, Rosita.

610
00:41:59.058 --> 00:42:00.810
You want to try with the helmet
this time?

611
00:42:00.893 --> 00:42:02.687
Oh, but now I know
what the dream meant.

612
00:42:02.770 --> 00:42:05.231
Yeah. She's afraid.

613
00:42:05.314 --> 00:42:07.233
She'll never be able to play the part.

614
00:42:07.316 --> 00:42:11.320
