and I'm not afraid at all.

615
00:42:11.404 --> 00:42:14.323
I can't just give you Rosita's part.
I mean...

616
00:42:14.866 --> 00:42:16.784
Moon, walk with me.

617
00:42:17.660 --> 00:42:20.580
