What, you got a kink in your think?

618
00:42:20.663 --> 00:42:22.790
It's just that I wrote
this part for Rosita and...

619
00:42:22.874 --> 00:42:24.500
Yeah. Let me tell you something, Moon.

620
00:42:24.584 --> 00:42:28.421
What you got here is an opportunity
to make me happy.

621
00:42:28.546 --> 00:42:30.548
And when an opportunity
like that comes along,

622
00:42:30.673 --> 00:42:32.008
