this is probably for the best.

649
00:43:26.270 --> 00:43:28.022
- Seriously?
- Seriously.

650
00:43:28.106 --> 00:43:30.358
I am completely fine with this.

651
00:43:37.198 --> 00:43:38.407
Hey, honey.

652
00:43:38.908 --> 00:43:41.744
Are you... you're sure you're not,
