but never mind.

672
00:44:48.102 --> 00:44:49.604
Seriously?

673
00:44:49.729 --> 00:44:51.564
Why do you have to be
so mean all the time?

674
00:44:51.647 --> 00:44:53.232
'Cause only when we suffer...

675
00:44:53.316 --> 00:44:55.318
