676
00:44:55.443 --> 00:44:57.236
Places, everyone!

677
00:44:57.361 --> 00:45:00.573
Ryan, you'll be playing his opponent
in the climax of the scene.

678
00:45:00.740 --> 00:45:01.908
Now...

679
00:45:02.742 --> 00:45:06.787
let's see if little Johnny
has learned the steps.

680
00:45:22.637 --> 00:45:23.971
Whoa. Sorry. Sorry, sorry.

681
00:45:24.555 --> 00:45:25.890
