00:50:01.582 --> 00:50:04.168
Oh, he's crazy.

754
00:50:04.251 --> 00:50:06.545
Pew. Pew, pew.

755
00:50:06.629 --> 00:50:08.005
- Wow, she's a mess.
- Pew, pew!

756
00:50:08.088 --> 00:50:11.050
- You're not gonna go out there, are you?
- Gonna have to. I mean...

757
00:50:11.133 --> 00:50:12.843
