771
00:51:01.850 --> 00:51:05.020
Take that, you nasty alien monster.

772
00:51:05.145 --> 00:51:07.189
Excuse me, but Mr. Crystal
wants to see you.

773
00:51:07.314 --> 00:51:09.275
Take that,
you nasty alien monster.

774
00:51:09.358 --> 00:51:12.361
- Well, I could come by this afternoon.
- He means now. Right now.

775
00:51:12.444 --> 00:51:14.905
Okay.

776
00:51:17.032 --> 00:51:20.119
- You wanted to see me, sir?
- Yes, I did. Yes, I did.

777
00:51:20.202 --> 00:51:22.079
- Come on in.
- Whoa.

778
00:51:22.162 --> 00:51:24.039
This place is incredible.

779
00:51:24.123 --> 00:51:25.582
Pretty great, huh?

780
00:51:26.208 --> 00:51:28.127
So, how's it going with Calloway?

781
00:51:28.377 --> 00:51:29.878
Calloway?

782
00:51:29.962 --> 00:51:31.922
It's, uh... it's good.

783
00:51:32.006 --> 00:51:33.757
- Yeah. Very good.
- Right, right.

784
00:51:34.466 --> 00:51:36.051
Well, let me ask you something.

785
00:51:36.135 --> 00:51:38.595
What did I do to make you
disrespect me, huh?

786
00:51:38.762 --> 00:51:39.680
What?

787
00:51:39.763 --> 00:51:42.599
Oh, what? You think I'm an idiot?
Some kind of bozo?

788
00:51:42.683 --> 00:51:44.935
No. No, sir, not at all.

789
00:51:45.019 --> 00:51:48.355
My team, they talked
to Calloway's lawyer,

790
00:51:48.439 --> 00:51:52.318
and they say he's never
heard of you or your show.

791
00:51:52.401 --> 00:51:54.528
Really? They said that? Uh...

792
00:51:54.653 --> 00:51:56.780
- You lied to me!
- I... I didn't mean to.

793
00:51:56.864 --> 00:51:59.074
Okay? Honestly, I really thought
I could get him.

794
00:51:59.158 --> 00:52:00.868
No one makes me look
like a fool! No one!

795
00:52:00.951 --> 00:52:03.162
I wouldn't dream of doing that to you.

796
00:52:03.245 --> 00:52:05.247
I swear, if you didn't have
my kid in your show,

797
00:52:05.331 --> 00:52:06.832
