I won't let you down, sir.

802
00:52:16.050 --> 00:52:18.635
Oh, I know you won't let me down.

803
00:52:19.053 --> 00:52:21.597
- Jerry, get in here!
- Yes, sir. Right here, sir.

804
00:52:21.680 --> 00:52:23.682
- Clean this mess up.
- Absolutely, I'd love to.

805
00:52:25.225 --> 00:52:28.103
Listen up. I got to go to Calloway's,
and I got to go ASAP.

806
00:52:28.187 --> 00:52:30.147
- Oh, no, please don't go there.
- Don't worry.

807
00:52:30.230 --> 00:52:32.358
I know you said he's crazy,
but I'll be all right.

808
00:52:32.441 --> 00:52:34.777
- Can I go with you, please?
- Uh, I don't know.

809
