818
00:52:52.503 --> 00:52:54.380
- Yes, I got to be tough.
- You got to be firm.

819
00:52:54.463 --> 00:52:55.923
Oh, and I got to be firm. Yes.

820
00:52:56.048 --> 00:52:56.965
And you cannot...

821
00:52:57.049 --> 00:53:00.010
I repeat, cannot let production
fall behind, not one little bit.

822
00:53:00.094 --> 00:53:02.596
- Is that clear?
- Yes, sir, Mr. Moon, sir.

823
00:53:10.187 --> 00:53:11.187
<i>Mason!</i>

824
00:53:11.230 --> 00:53:13.857
<i>That volcano should've been
finished yesterday!</i>

825
00:53:13.982 --> 00:53:16.318
- We're on it, Miss Crawly.
<i>- You better be!</i>

826
00:53:16.443 --> 00:53:17.653
<i>Meena, Darius,</i>

827
00:53:17.736 --> 00:53:21.198
