844
00:54:22.885 --> 00:54:24.720
No! Stay off the fence!

845
00:54:24.803 --> 00:54:26.930
Don't listen to him.

846
00:55:00.088 --> 00:55:01.381
<i>Stop, stop, stop!</i>

847
00:55:01.465 --> 00:55:03.467
