888
00:57:14.056 --> 00:57:15.474
Oh, my gosh.

889
00:57:15.557 --> 00:57:17.434
- Have you talked to him yet?
- Uh-huh.

890
00:57:17.559 --> 00:57:19.436
- You have?
- We were just discussing

