being in our show.

892
00:57:21.438 --> 00:57:22.439
What did he say?

893
00:57:22.522 --> 00:57:24.316
He said no.

894
00:57:24.650 --> 00:57:27.486
Not in a million years.

895
00:57:29.112 --> 00:57:30.739
Please, Mr. Calloway.

896
00:57:30.822 --> 00:57:32.616
Look, you don't...

