978
01:02:38.088 --> 01:02:39.756
Oh, and I have something for you.

979
01:02:39.923 --> 01:02:41.174
Thank you, Mr. Moon, sir.

980
01:02:41.258 --> 01:02:43.510
All right, you can ease off
the attitude now.

981
01:02:43.677 --> 01:02:45.303
Oh, oh, yes, yes.

982
01:02:45.387 --> 01:02:47.681
